Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.12,0:33:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,consciousness, the rate of happiness\Nclimbs till it's finally 100%.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.00,0:33:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh because you're easier go easygoing\Nand because the source of your joy comes
