Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.15,0:34:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,what he's saying.\NIf I get in trouble with him, I'm in
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.76,0:34:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,real trouble. So,\Nokay, doc, you have your way with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.11,0:34:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The rate of criminality, you see, the\Nlower level of consciousness is almost
