Dialogue: 0,1:06:25.35,1:06:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,me. Uh well when you say a good job in\Nwhat way? You mean mathemat you know as
Dialogue: 0,1:06:33.76,1:06:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,far as money goes? Do you mean as far as\Nusing your talents? You mean as far as
Dialogue: 0,1:06:37.28,1:06:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,the future? So you have to be precise in\Nyour question and you have to have a
Dialogue: 0,1:06:43.28,1:06:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,detached. You can't have a vested\Ninterest in trying to prove or disprove
Dialogue: 0,1:06:48.79,1:06:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,something. you know, if we had a vested\Ninterest in hating China and communism
Dialogue: 0,1:06:53.76,1:06:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,and all, we wouldn't be able to get, you\Nknow, that frankly the
